        <Parent_String>cultural landscapes by location or context [300132446], cultural landscapes [300008932], landscapes (environments) [300008626], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
